{"tid":1825048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(警世) 留意敵對陣營新文宣方向 【外國左翼】","createTime":"2020-01-15T03:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T04:48:41.000Z","uid":57044,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6469d47f075d9d4a9c66fe75d8876d502528792","tid":1825048,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"今日無意中收到廢老老母一段片，係港人港地，大家睇完記得幫手report, down vote 再睇我內文。<br />\n<strong>美國記者安德烈給香港年輕人的一封信</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6PojIrWJ9kM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6PojIrWJ9kM&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=8dc81501\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6PojIrWJ9kM</a><br />\n<br />\n我睇左十秒段片就無睇，之後去google下個記者，之後搵到個記者英文名係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Andre Vltchek</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n 以下係我搵到一啲佢寫既文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.unz.com/avltchek/why-i-stand-by-the-70-years-old-communist-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unz.com%2Favltchek%2Fwhy-i-stand-by-the-70-years-old-communist-china%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=e74ed796\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.unz.com/avltchek/why-i-stand-by-the-70-years-old-communist-china/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjH56jC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjH56jC.jpg&h=3daa7b65&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n內容大概係祝賀中共70歲大壽，中共同俄羅斯係對抗歐美帝國主義力量，永不放棄，佢好欣賞中共對抗西方資本主義。<br />\n<br />\n呢類人係外國可以話係新左翼，小弟讀書時都有讀，其中最多人讀係法蘭克福學派(Frankfurt school), 另外搵到呢個記者好支持 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Noam Chomsky</span></strong>。 可能有啲手足唔識佢，但呢個人係學術界好出名，甚至可以話享負盛名，但佢支持赤柬屠殺，911等事件，所以呢類人好危險，係西方一大隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n我講咁多想帶出係，係西方，猶奇係美國同西歐，佢地已經去到後資本年代，好多人對資本主義同民主抱有懷疑，可以話係陷入左失樂園，有批人開始掉返落去信奉極權同共產。<br />\n<br />\n對於外國，特別美國黎講，新左翼係一大威脅。香港如果可以幫到佢地剷除到佢地國民對共產既美好幻想，西方會更加出力幫我地。世界政治就好似做生意，我地幫到人，人地先會幫我地。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Ask not what the country can do for you, ask what you can do for your country&quot; JF Kennedy <br />\n<br />\n大家幫手打Twitter 戰線，主要工作就係搵出呢啲共狗間諜，可以sd比美國右翼政客。大家要重視呢啲資訊，重點唔係港人港地呢啲廢老page，而係西方勢力無我地想像中咁團結，如果歐美右翼失勢，香港台灣，甚至全世界都會陷入萬劫不復。所以，要提防呢班共匪既毒思想，同於而家反侵班西方年輕人影響好大。"},{"pid":"ef0bacbf6c8cd1fc386121cfc66f9667d7c5ecd5","tid":1825048,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70a62d95d806ad2d43f2640ee760edad00a6f027","tid":1825048,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"咩心態嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fb5aac41697e1f8d417195571a4d4ab8d684dd","tid":1825048,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70a62d95d806ad2d43f2640ee760edad00a6f027","tid":1825048,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"咩心態嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"你指邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab2c2aecd789f039fd732d614aa9100e433caef","tid":1825048,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18fb5aac41697e1f8d417195571a4d4ab8d684dd","tid":1825048,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70a62d95d806ad2d43f2640ee760edad00a6f027","tid":1825048,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"咩心態嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"你指邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos